Name:           python-sphinx-bootstrap-theme
Version:        0.7.1
Release:        0
Summary:        Sphinx Bootstrap Theme
License:        MIT AND Apache-2.0
Group:          Development/Languages/Python
URL:            http://ryan-roemer.github.com/sphinx-bootstrap-theme/README.html
